title: The Internet Is Saying This Guy Keying Cars In London Looks AN AWFUL LOT LIKE TRUMP — Does He? [VIDEO]
text:
A video recently posted to Facebook shows some random bloke keying cars in London. 
WATCH: 
Posted by Kay Hussain on Sunday, March 5, 2017 
A close up of the CCTV footage shows that the perp bears more than a passing resemblance to the 45th President of the United States, Donald J. Trump. 
WATCH: 
Posted by Kay Hussain on Sunday, March 5, 2017 
“Mother fuker [sic],” commented Abul Hasnat. 
“Dirty pedeophile scum bad mined cunt are te sure its not donult thrump lol scum [sic],” added Natasha Lvs John Mcdonagh. 
What do you think? Does this car keying a$$hole look like Donald Trump?
